function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)
	-- Cave collapse, characters enter	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(actorCaveIn, fxCollapse)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVigo01, locV1, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVigo01, locV1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorNeyrelle01, locN1, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(actorCaveIn, fxCollapse)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Ney runs to ledge
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorNeyrelle01, locN2, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorNeyrelle01, locN2)
	
	-- Vigo runs to ledge
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorVigo01, 1.25)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVigo01, locV2, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVigo01, locV2)

	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	followerVigo = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_VIGO_FOLLOWER)
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_NEYRELLE_FOLLOWER)
	
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVigoLift1, followerVigo)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	followerVigo = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_VIGO_FOLLOWER)
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_NEYRELLE_FOLLOWER)

	-- Hoist anims begin
	Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStart(gizmoHoist_platform)
	Hydra.ChargeableGizmoStart(gizmoHoist_suspension)
	
	-- Neyrelle move action
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleAtHoist, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, locNeyrelleAtHoist)
	end
	
	-- Vigo move action
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerVigo, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerVigo)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerVigo, locVigoAtHoist, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerVigo, locVigoAtHoist)
	end
	
	--"Lift is fixed, let's go home."/"No, old man." conversation
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.CancelConversation(convVigoLift1)
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVigoLift2, followerVigo)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Actor Setup
	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerVigo)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	followerVigo = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_VIGO_FOLLOWER)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVigoLift0, followerVigo)
	end
end
